  <p>These General Terms and Conditions ("GTC") apply to all offers and contracts for services by eFlury Consulting, owner Emanuel Aaron Flury, Keltenweg 4, 2540 Grenchen, Switzerland ("we"). Our offers are directed exclusively at businesses and self-employed professionals (B2B), not at consumers.</p>

