      <li>Where liability exists, it is <strong>limited in aggregate to the fee actually paid for the affected project</strong>; for recurring services, to the fees paid in the last 12 months.</li>
      <li><strong>Liability for indirect and consequential damage is excluded to the extent permitted by law</strong> — in particular lost profit, business interruption, third-party claims, and data loss to the extent it would have been avoidable through industry-standard backups.</li>
